{"tid":1293923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣傳，呢日係旺角七七戒嚴","createTime":"2019-07-07T17:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:16:35.000Z","uid":103521,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e762b8ae1d43887ec695a701ad05d09d09c75bfb","tid":1293923,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:11:36.000Z","msg":"香港交接後既第一次既戒嚴<br />\n<br />\n明明遊行和平行，警狗一邊開mic叫人離開叫人退，但另一邊又直接封曬街既左右困住中間d人唔比人走，又警棍扑到人爆血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個旺角都照鎖照封，記者做野都比人趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾個軍裝大男人，可以騎撚住個女仔黎制服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十幾隻軍裝圍住一個示威者黎打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶走被捕者，可以不斷禁同扯佢個頭同頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警狗可以唔帶證已經係奇聞，依家直接帶個頭盔就可以清人場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n譚文豪議員係封鎖線外，都照比一堆警攞3/4個大聲公聲力竭警告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncommendor龜縮係後面唔肯出黎，前線又可以申曬頭出黎發鬧炸鬧人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成條線得番記者，成堆警狗用長盾衝擊記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一夜之間，又見到香港黑警更墜落腐化既一面，警權比三權擁有更高既地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死黑警我真係屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"a90b85479737c8947fc5c8d25f2d54d028b91fe1","tid":1293923,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}